<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="shortly-adv">shortly <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ʃɔːtli/    美 /'ʃɔːrtli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>立刻；不久：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He finished a difficult task on his own <strong>shortly after</strong> he entered the company.
他进公司后不久就独立完成了一项艰巨的任务。</p></div></div>